episodes.title: Exposing The Cult Of Red Pill Masculinity
episodes.description: The Cult of Red Pill Masculinity has gotten out of hand. With influencers like Andrew Tate, Hamza Ahmed, Sneako, and Myron Gains (Fresh and Fit Podcast) dragging men down a self improvement hole. Mario Rios goes over red pill ideas on dating, women, success, and happiness.
